(14, 1, '2021-04-04 17:34:59', '2021-04-04 17:34:59', '<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide\" id=\"about-cities-air\"><!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading alignwide\"></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Personally, I have suffered from respiratory issues since coming to Abu Dhabi. As a result, I did research into air pollution and developed the habit of tracking air quality daily to minimize my exposure. Inadvertently, this process of becoming a citizen scientist has made me more aware of the dire situation of air pollution juxtaposed with low awareness and action-taking within the community and the region as a whole.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The isolated location of schools and universities campuses, like NYU Abu Dhabi, gives us a sense of comfort and cleanliness: we are not constantly surrounded by vehicles or factories. The issue of air pollution thus gets selectively compartmentalized. It is hard to pay attention to the air we breathe in, it is not a priority. Little do we know, air pollution from traffic, industries, oil refineries, and sandstorms in other parts of the country and in neighboring countries can disperse all over the region, regardless of proximity to emission source.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><cite><em>A word from the author</em></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As air quality and air pollution can be complicated topics, this guide is divided into bite-site articles that can help you become familiar with some of the terminologies and ways to protect your respiratory well-beings. It is definitely not an exhaustive nor a must-do list. You can always refer to <strong><a href=\"#further-reading\" data-type=\"internal\" data-id=\"#further-reading\">Further Reading</a></strong> for more detailed breakdowns and visualizations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"../what-is-particulate-matter/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"../what-is-particulate-matter/\">1. What is particulate matter air pollution?</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left\"><a href=\"../particulate-matter-in-abu-dhabi/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"../particulate-matter-in-abu-dhabi/\">2. Particulate matter in Abu Dhabi</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"../ways-to-protect-yourself/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"../ways-to-protect-yourself/\">3. Ways to protect yourself</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading alignwide\" id=\"further-reading\">Further Reading</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Detailed data visualization and analysis of air pollution for all countries: <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ourworldindata.org/outdoor-air-pollution\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://ourworldindata.org/outdoor-air-pollution\" target=\"_blank\">Outdoor Air Pollution</a></strong>, Our World in Data</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Stories of air pollution from all over the world:<br><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://undark.org/breathtaking/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://undark.org/breathtaking/\" target=\"_blank\">The Weight of Numbers: Air Pollution and PM2.5</a></strong>, Undark</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>By combining photographs – qualitative evidence, with quantitative graphs, Reuters succeeded in bridging the gap between the physicality of air pollution and scientific data:<br><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://graphics.reuters.com/INDIA-POLLUTION/01008173281/index.html\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://graphics.reuters.com/INDIA-POLLUTION/01008173281/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">A window into Delhi’s deadly pollution</a></strong>, Reuter Graphics</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>How the COVID-19 pandemic inadvertently improve air quality across the world:<br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://graphics.reuters.com/CLIMATE-CHANGE/CORONAVIRUS-POLLUTION/jznvngjyplm/index.html\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://graphics.reuters.com/CLIMATE-CHANGE/CORONAVIRUS-POLLUTION/jznvngjyplm/index.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>A breath of fresh air</strong></a>, Reuter Graphics</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>... with more to be updated</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'CITIESair Blog - A Guide to Take Care of Your Respiratory Health', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2023-10-12 23:08:51', '2023-10-12 19:08:51', '', 0, 'https://nyuadair.com/?page_id=14', 0, 'page', '', 0),
